2198871978.query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contributions WHERE ((status_geom_type).geom_type = 'Polygon' OR (status_geom_type).geom_type = 'MultiPolygon') AND tags ? 'building' AND NOT tags @> '{"building": "no"}' AND area >= 1E6
